<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.3.7">
<l>mulaiyētum vēṇṭēṉeṉ ṟōṭiniṉ kātiṟ</l>
<l rend="indent">kaṭippaip paṟitteṟin tiṭṭu</l>
<l>malaiyai yeṭuttu makiḻntu kaṉmāri</l>
<l rend="indent">kāttup pacunirai mēyttāy</l>
<l>cilaiyoṉ ṟiṟuttāy tirivik kiramā</l>
<l rend="indent">tiruvāyar pāṭip pirāṉē</l>
<l>talainilāp pōtēyuṉ kātaip perukkātē</l>
<l rend="indent">viṭṭiṭṭēṉ kuṟṟamē yeṉṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who, running [wild] saying,</l>
<l rend="indent">“I don’t want [your] breast [or] anything else”,</l>
<l rend="indent">plucking the earrings from your ears and throwing [them],</l>
<l>grazed the cow herd and, joyfully raising a mountain,</l>
<l>protected [them] from a shower of stones!</l>
<l>You broke the bow! O Trivikkrama!</l>
<l>O Lord of the holy cowherd village!</l>
<l>I gave up without causing the increase to your ear. It is my fault!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
